  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Previous studies have reported that about 3 % of patients who have had open inguinal
      herniorrhaphy had a visceral, ejaculatory-related pain.

      The investigators want to assess this problem among patients after laparoscopic inguinal
      hernia repair with(self-administered questionnaire study).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
